parameters: ...No response. Did they escape... or is it too late...

Welcome to Hatayaki Village!... That's what it says. I
wonder what will happen to this village from now on.

\SE[52] (This person is still breathing... \!\SE[38] but
this is already... over...)

\SE[52](W-What should I do... \!\SE[53]That person...
they're already \.beyond saving.)

\SE[59](I-I need to hurry...! My father, my mother... Laura
too...)

What... are you just going to abandon me...? Then, as a
replacement...

Please... kill me instead... I'm already... so cold, I can't
see... I'm scared. I know... that I'm already... beyond
help...

I know that uniform. It's the Black Uniform, right? If it's
you, you should be able to do it easily... right?

Please... make it easier for me... I'm scared of just
waiting to die... Please... I'm begging you... I'm begging
you...
I'll make it easy for you

\SE[52]I-I'm sorry...! \!\SE[23]I can't... do something like
that...!!

...! Hey... where are you going...!! Why won't you help
me...!!!
Get out of the way...! Don't interfere with me...!!!

Here is a fun pig! Let's touch it and become happy with its
warmth!

I am growing corn for pig farming. Theft is a crime. You
should never do it. Don't you think it's pitiful to see cute
pigs go hungry?

The crops have been destroyed... It's probably impossible to
use them as food anymore.

The bonfire in Hatayaki Village's number one spot doesn't
seem to have gone out yet. I feel a little energized. My
stamina has fully recovered.
